      "description": "Absolutely breathtaking! This vehicle is in true showroom condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it was first sold. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, this is a rare find for any collector or enthusiast seeking perfection. It's a turn-key masterpiece ready for its next home!",
