    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or aging. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. This is a collector-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in perfect, original state.",
