    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and bodywork to be roadworthy again. The engine struggles to maintain idle, the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, and there are various leaks throughout the undercarriage. Cosmetically, the exterior has several large dents and patches of rust, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This car is best suited as a project for a dedicated mechanic or for parts.",
